{{Page version|42.5.1}}
The <code>ToolTip</code> parameter is used to define the description of the recipe. This parameter will refer to a translation key in the translation files (see [[Translations]]).

==Example==
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
ToolTip = Tooltip_Recipe_MyRecipe,
}}

And in the translation file:
{{CodeSnip
| lang = lua
| code =
Tooltip_EN = {
    Tooltip_Recipe_MyRecipe = "This is a description of my recipe",
}
}}
